('0b62a07c-bf1f-4500-822a-cf138527bedd', 'f96b7086-1fde-47e6-930a-05585c797a7a', '1', '{"title": "政治博弈扰动能源政策，AI算力产业链成本与格局重塑(Political Turbulence Distorts Energy Policy, Reshaping Costs and Structure in the AI Computing Industry Chain)", "rating": null, "ticker": null, "analysts": [{"role": 1, "analyst_id": "58020af7-0844-471d-ad19-6b66a73178b6", "sort_order": 1}], "sector_id": null, "coverage_id": null, "region_code": null, "report_type": "macro", "target_price": null, "report_language": "zh", "contact_person_id": null, "investment_thesis": "<p class=\"16\" style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">事件</span></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">在</span>2026<span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">年</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">3</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">月的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">美国</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">参议院辩论中</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">参议院民主党人对共和党的标志性</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">《拯救美国法案》（</span>SAVE America Act<span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">）</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">提出了数百项修正案，其中包括二十多项涉及能源与自然资源问题的提案。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">这些举措是民主党推迟并破坏</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">该</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">争议性</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">选举安全法案</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">努力的一部分。该法案旨在增加非公民在联邦选举中投票的难度，而民主党则认为，这将使数百万美国公民更难行使投票权</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">。目前民主党人提出的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">修正案包括：废除总统唐纳德</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">&middot;</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">特朗普关于能源与气候变化的行政命令；延长某些可再生能源的税收抵免；以及要求数据中心运营商报告其能源与水资源的消耗情况。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">本次民主党在《拯救美国法案》中塞入大量能源相关修正案，本质是一场典型的国会政治博弈，而非真正意义上的能源政策立法。</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"16\" style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">点评</span></span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"16\" style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">能源政策高度政治化，两党共识持续瓦解，长期规划能力被严重削弱。</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">能源议题已深度嵌入美国党派竞争，政策稳定性持续弱化，行业与资本面临的不确定性显著上升。无论是气候目标、电力结构、补贴政策还是监管规则，都越来越成为选举工具，而非基于产业现实与能源安全的理性安排。民主党借能源议题绑定民生情绪、共和党则强调成本与供给稳定，双方在核心方向上难以形成长期一致，导致政策频繁摇摆、预期反复修正。这种环境下，大型能源基建、电网改造、新型电力项目的投资周期被拉长，风险成本抬升，跨周期资本开支意愿明显下降，公用事业与能源产业链整体估值逻辑被迫向</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">&ldquo;短期确定性&rdquo;倾斜。</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"16\" style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">数据中心等高耗能产业的成本规则正在重塑，</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">&ldquo;用者自付&rdquo;将成为长期趋势。</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">伴随</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">AI</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">算力爆发式增长，数据中心用电负荷快速扩张，电网扩容与供电压力持续上升，过去由全民分摊电力基础设施成本的模式难以为继。政策层面正在加速转向</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">&ldquo;谁受益、谁承担&rdquo;的定价机制，数据中心将更多独立承担电网接入、线路扩容、备用容量等相关成本。以</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">100MW</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">数据中心测算：电网接入与扩容成本约</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">亿</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">-1.5</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">亿美元，电价上调</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">15%-20%</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">将带来年电费增加约</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">1000</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">万</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">-1500</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">万美元，全生命周期成本抬升</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">10%-15%</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">。这会直接推高行业整体资本开支与运营成本，倒逼产业向更高能效、绿电配套、储能协同、分布式供能方向升级，低效小型项目逐步出清，行业集中度与技术门槛同步抬升。</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"16\" style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">政策内耗与成本上行，正在缓慢侵蚀美国在全球算力与再工业化竞争中的优势。</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">能源政策不稳定直接拖累电网现代化进度，电力成本刚性上涨又进一步提高制造业与数字产业的运营压力。跨国资本在布局长期算力基地、先进制造产能时，会更加谨慎评估美国市场的政策风险与综合成本。虽然短期仍有产业集群与技术生态支撑，但中长期看，持续的政治博弈与成本抬升，会逐步削弱其整体产业竞争力，也让能源转型与产业升级的节奏慢于潜在最优路径。</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"16\" style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">投资建议</span></span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"15\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">受益北美电网升级与智能调度需求，配网自动化与高压设备订单持续增长的电网智能化与电力设备商如【</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">GE Vernova</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">】、【</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">Eaton</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">】、【</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">Schneider Electric</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">】、【</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">ABB</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">】，数据中心热管理与供电商如【</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">Vertiv</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">】，储能供应商【</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">Tesla</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">】，离网发电制造商如【</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">Bloom Energy</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">】、【潍柴动力】。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"16\" style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">风险</span></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 2.1pt; margin-left: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 13pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #000000; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: #000000; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">能源政策博弈加剧，政策不明确性上升；</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: #000000; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">智能化技术电网应用效果不及预期；</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: #000000; font-size: 16px;\">AI</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: #000000; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">用电需求低于预期。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 5pt 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">In March 2026, Senate Democrats introduced over 20 energy-related amendments to the Republican SAVE America Act (a federal election security bill). These proposals, ranging from rolling back Trump&rsquo;s climate orders to mandating data center energy reporting, aim to delay the bill while highlighting partisan divides over voting rights and energy policy.</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">While unlikely to pass given the GOP majority, these amendments serve two tactical goals: voter alignment, linking voting access to climate/energy costs, and political exposure, forcing Republicans to vote against popular consumer protections.</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">The backdrop is a crisis in energy affordability. With 2025 retail electricity prices jumping 6.7% (far outpacing CPI), the surge in AI data center demand and re-industrialization has made grid-upgrade costs a core 2026 policy issue. While Democrats favor regulation, the GOP&rsquo;s \"Ratepayer Protection Pledge\" forces \"Hyperscalers\" (Amazon, Google, Meta) to fund their own infrastructure. This shifts the U.S. power model from \"socialized costs\" to a \"beneficiary-pays\" system.</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;<span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">We observed </span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">structural certainty in three areas:</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">Grid Modernization</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;Data Center Efficiency/Thermal Management</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">; </span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">Off-grid/Distributed Generation.</span></p>", "certificate_confirmed": true}', 'f96b7086-1fde-47e6-930a-05585c797a7a/f96b7086-1fde-47e6-930a-05585c797a7a_001_report_2026-04-02T08-07-05-129Z____________AI_____________AutoRefresh.docx', null, '6de69f70-b17a-48e1-8e49-3efa86b68c40', '2026-04-02 16:07:05.903589+08', '2026-04-02 16:07:05.903589+08', '政治博弈扰动能源政策，AI算力产业链成本与格局重塑_AutoRefresh.docx', null, null, null);
