('9baf60e1-72f7-4a6c-b79b-51dd3067369c', 'c5869ebc-4e25-40bc-9df8-d2a20977a988', '1', '{"title": "全球国防与航空航天周报(03/22-03/28): 航空航天领域沿多主线演进，全球安全局势高位震荡，地缘冲突加速防务投入(Aerospace Sector Evolves Along Multiple Lines, Global Security Tensions Elevated, Geopolitical Conflicts Boost Defense Spending)", "rating": null, "ticker": null, "analysts": [{"role": 1, "analyst_id": "58020af7-0844-471d-ad19-6b66a73178b6", "sort_order": 1}], "sector_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000087", "coverage_id": null, "region_code": "HK", "report_type": "sector", "target_price": null, "report_language": "zh", "contact_person_id": null, "investment_thesis": "<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: #1f497d; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">核心观点：</span></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: #1f497d; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">全球国防与航空航天：</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">美国：飞机发动机和发动机部件制造价格指数</span>2026<span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">年</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">2</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">月为</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">277.110</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">，环比</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">+0.03%</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">，同比增长</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">1.07%</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">。飞机发动机和发动机零部件制造：飞机发动机零部件价格指数</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">2026</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">年</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">2</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">月为</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">293.396</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">，环比</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">+0.05%</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">，同比增长</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">1.41%</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">。美国政府支出国防价格指数</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">2025</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">年</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">Q4</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">为</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">120.187</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">，环比</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">+0.9%</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">，同比增长</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">2.95%</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">本周航空航天领域在地缘冲突对民航全链条的冲击、航空安全监管深化、商用飞机市场竞争格局重塑、全球航天发射与深空探测多点突破</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">多条</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">主线上同步演进。中东局势持续推高燃油成本与空域不确定性，全球航司密集调整航线与运力；</span>FAA<span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">完成波音宽体机适航认证，安全监管体系不断完善；空客接连斩获大额窄体机订单，在供应链与技术维度持续扩大竞争优势；航天方面，</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">NASA</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">发布土星与超新星探测成果，俄罗斯推进空间站补给任务。行业整体正迈向更强风险韧性、更严安全标准与更深层技术驱动的新阶段。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">本周全球安全局势高位震荡，北美、欧洲与中东三大战略方向同步强化防务投入。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">美国持续加码</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;<span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">&ldquo;Golden Dome&rdquo; </span></span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">天基反导体系，推动日本深度融入项目研发体系</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">；欧洲密集部署防务资金，自主建设面临安全与技术双重考验；中东局势持续升级，防空反导、远程打击与战机升级需求快速释放，成为全球防务订单增长核心热点。全球防务采购加速向一体化防空反导、无人作战、先进空战平台及战场感知等核心领域集中，行业正迎来短期订单释放、长期技术迭代与全球防务格局深度重构并行的新阶段。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: #1f497d; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">投资建议：</span></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: #1f497d; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">随着航空航天业的稳健复苏、国防支出增加及军事现代化需求，我们建议关注高性能结构部件制造商</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">Howmet Aerospace</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">、航空航天零部件专业制造商</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">Loar Holdings</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">、法国航空发动机巨头赛峰</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">(SAFRY)</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">、领先国防承包商雷神技术</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">(RTX)</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">及以色列国防电子龙头</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">Elbit Systems</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">。随着民用航空器维护需求增加，我们建议关注</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">VSE</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">技术服务公司</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: #1f497d; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">风险提示：</span></span></strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">地缘冲突持续升级，民航运营成本与航线网络面临较大不确定性</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">；</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">防务项目审批及资金拨付进度存在滞后可能</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">；</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">商用飞机供应链恢复与适航认证节奏或影响交付计划</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">；</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">商业航天资本市场预期与项目落地节奏存在错配，发射服务价格面临下行压力</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">；</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">关键技术突破与多国工业分工协调存在滞后风险</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">Global Defense &amp; Aerospace</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">Price Indices: </span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">The U.S. aircraft engine and engine parts manufacturing price index was 277.110 in February 2026, up 0.03% MoM and 1.07% YoY; aircraft engine components price index stood at 293.396, up 0.05% MoM and 1.41% YoY. The U.S. government defense spending price index was 120.187 in Q4 2025, up 0.9% QoQ and 2.95% YoY.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">Aerospace</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">Commercial Space: </span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">The ongoing tensions in the Middle East continue to drive up fuel costs and heighten airspace uncertainties, prompting global airlines to intensively adjust routes and capacity. The FAA has completed airworthiness certification for Boeing wide-body aircraft, with safety regulatory frameworks continuously improving. Airbus has secured multiple large-scale narrow-body aircraft orders, steadily expanding its competitive edge in supply chain management and technological innovation. In aerospace developments, NASA announced breakthroughs in Saturn and supernova exploration, while Russia advanced its space station resupply missions.</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">Defense</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">Defense Budget: </span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">The three strategic regions of North America, Europe, and the Middle East are simultaneously ramping up defense investments. </span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">The U.S. has further ramped up efforts on its \"Golden Dome\" space-based missile defense system and deepened Japan&rsquo;s participation in the program&rsquo;s research and development</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">. Europe is pouring substantial defense funds into domestic projects, yet faces dual challenges in security and technological capabilities. Meanwhile, the Middle East's escalating tensions have triggered a surge in demand for air defense systems, long-range strike capabilities, and advanced fighter jets, making it a key driver of global defense order growth.</span></span></p>", "certificate_confirmed": true}', 'c5869ebc-4e25-40bc-9df8-d2a20977a988/c5869ebc-4e25-40bc-9df8-d2a20977a988_001_report_2026-04-02T08-27-57-511Z_______________0322-0328_____________________________________AutoRefresh__1_.docx', null, '6de69f70-b17a-48e1-8e49-3efa86b68c40', '2026-04-02 16:27:58.21547+08', '2026-04-02 16:27:58.21547+08', '华福国际全球国防和航空航天（0322-0328)：航空航天领域沿多主线演进，全球安全局势高位震荡，地缘冲突加速防务投入_AutoRefresh (1).docx', null, null, null);
INSERT INTO "public"."report_version" ("id", "report_id", "version_no", "snapshot_json", "word_file_path", "model_file_path", "changed_by", "changed_at", "created_at", "word_file_name", "model_file_name", "pdf_file_path", "pdf_file_name") VALUES 
('9ddef1d5-c463-4370-90ec-d5dfb7883aae', 'be1ea2a1-bdc2-47ea-8fee-071b30d19221', '1', '{"title": "中东冲突范围外溢至双线航道：胡塞武装行动叠加特朗普停战预期，曼德海峡能源航道持续承压(Escalating Mideast Conflict Spills to Dual Lanes: Houthi Action & Trump Ceasefire Signals Pressure Bab el-Mandeb Energy Lanes)", "rating": null, "ticker": null, "analysts": [{"role": 1, "analyst_id": "58020af7-0844-471d-ad19-6b66a73178b6", "sort_order": 1}], "sector_id": null, "coverage_id": null, "region_code": null, "report_type": "macro", "target_price": null, "report_language": "zh", "contact_person_id": null, "investment_thesis": "<p><strong>事件</strong></p><p>2026 年3月28 日，也门胡塞武装正式宣布对以色列实施持续导弹打击，中东冲突由波斯湾—霍尔木兹海峡扩散至红海—曼德海峡，全球两大能源航运咽喉同步承压。进入4月初，美国总统特朗普释放停战信号，但表态与战场行动明显背离，伊朗、胡塞武装未停止行动，以色列军事行动进一步升级，地缘局势仍处于高度混沌状态。霍尔木兹海峡承担全球约&nbsp;1/5 石油消费与&nbsp;1/5 LNG 贸易运输，航运受阻态势未改；沙特经延布港—曼德海峡的替代通道处于袭击威胁范围内，能源缓冲机制持续承压，地缘风险仍主导全球资产定价。</p><p><strong>点评</strong></p><p><strong>冲突由单点扩散至双线，地缘战略不确定性显著抬升。</strong>胡塞武装正式介入使中东冲突形成霍尔木兹海峡&nbsp;+ 曼德海峡双压力点，地缘对抗复杂化，区域稳定机制弱化。本次两大能源航道同时承压，为近50年能源史罕见，冲击量级远超单一海峡风险事件。伊朗以综合方式应对，美国战略层面被动，美、以、伊三方国内局势、领导层公信力与经济状况均面临压力，政权命运相互交织。谈判双方诉求分歧显著，美方条件与伊方核心诉求难以快速弥合，美国选举政治与中东战局相互交织，进一步加剧政策波动与尾部风险。整体来看，中东地缘格局进入持续重塑阶段，全球资产将长期包含更高地缘风险溢价，风险偏好持续下行，避险资产相对占优。</p><p><strong>两大能源咽喉同时暴露风险，供应弹性收缩，价格与流向体系重构。</strong>依据EIA与Kpler&nbsp;2026 年3月最新航运数据，霍尔木兹海峡与曼德海峡合计承担全球海运石油贸易约30%–35%，为全球能源供给核心命脉。其中，霍尔木兹海峡日均运量约2090万桶，占全球海运石油贸易25%；曼德海峡日均运量420万–490万桶，占比5%–8%。冲突升级后，沙特经红海延布港&nbsp;— 曼德海峡原油出口快速攀升，3 月日均升至&nbsp;340 万桶/日，峰值突破&nbsp;500 万桶&nbsp;/ 日，较冲突前增长近3倍，成为对冲霍尔木兹海峡受阻的关键替代通道，但该线路已处于胡塞武装火力覆盖范围，能源缓冲机制面临直接考验。全球原油流向出现结构性切换，俄罗斯经曼德海峡出口大幅回落，沙特供给持续抢占亚洲市场。双线受压导致油轮绕行航程增加10–14天，综合运输成本抬升30%–50%，战争险保费暴涨超10倍，供应链风险外溢推升能源价格与通胀压力，显著制约全球货币政策空间。</p><p><strong>油价大幅冲高并定价航道风险，全球市场转向防御配置。</strong>红海与曼德海峡风险推升原油溢价，布伦特原油冲高至&nbsp;116.4 美元/桶，月度涨幅接近&nbsp;59%，创下&nbsp;1990 年海湾战争以来最强单月上涨，航道受阻风险已被市场充分定价。当前航线结构呈现明显分化：沙特红海通道运输保持通畅，俄罗斯经曼德海峡流向大幅回落，全球原油流向切换趋势明确。双线航道受压进一步收紧油轮运力、抬升运输成本，油价易涨难跌格局巩固。尽管特朗普释放停战信号，但市场对和平预期保持谨慎，油价下行空间有限。高油价持续推升全球通胀与增长压力，资本市场风险偏好下行，能源、航运等板块确定性优势突出，高估值成长板块持续承压，全球资金配置主线全面转向防御与安全优先。</p><p><strong>投资建议</strong></p><p>我们建议关注全球原油运输核心龙头企业【Frontline Ltd.】、【<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"http://CMB.TECH\">CMB.TECH</a> NV】、【Teekay Tankers】；全球集装箱与能源航运龙头企业【A.P. Moller-Maersk】、【Hapag-Lloyd】；国际上游油气生产与能源巨头企业【Exxon Mobil】、【Chevron】、【ConocoPhillips】；以及全球油服与能源设备服务龙头企业【SLB】、【Halliburton】。</p><p><strong>风险</strong></p><p>中东地缘冲突超预期缓和，航道恢复导致油价、航运运价回落，绕行溢价收窄；全球滞胀加剧，原油需求萎缩抵消供给收缩支撑；能源航运板块估值随地缘情绪波动，投资不确定性提升。</p><p>On March 28, 2026, Yemen’s Houthi movement expanded the Middle East conflict to the Strait of Hormuz and Bab el-Mandeb/Red Sea, putting two key global energy chokepoints under pressure. In early April, U.S. President Trump signaled a ceasefire, but tensions remained elevated on the ground.&nbsp;The two chokepoints account for 30%–35% of global seaborne oil trade. Shipping disruptions have lifted costs and war risk premiums, while Saudi Arabia’s Red Sea crude exports have surged sharply. Brent crude jumped to $116.4/bbl, up nearly 59% month-on-month.&nbsp;Geopolitical uncertainty will persist, keeping energy markets volatile and supporting defensive allocations to energy and shipping.</p>", "certificate_confirmed": true}', 'be1ea2a1-bdc2-47ea-8fee-071b30d19221/be1ea2a1-bdc2-47ea-8fee-071b30d19221_001_report_2026-04-01T12-28-05-015Z_2026-1_April____________________________________________AutoRefresh.docx', null, '6de69f70-b17a-48e1-8e49-3efa86b68c40', '2026-04-01 20:28:05.310941+08', '2026-04-01 20:28:05.310941+08', '2026-1+April：中东冲突范围外溢至双线航道：胡塞武装行动叠加特朗普停战预期，曼德海峡能源航道持续承压_AutoRefresh.docx', null, null, null);
INSERT INTO "public"."report_version" ("id", "report_id", "version_no", "snapshot_json", "word_file_path", "model_file_path", "changed_by", "changed_at", "created_at", "word_file_name", "model_file_name", "pdf_file_path", "pdf_file_name") VALUES 
('a275655c-606f-4976-8a13-10b5a0f683f0', 'dff9e78a-d3cb-42f2-ac0c-aaaab2a06fe4', '2', '{"title": "政治博弈扰动能源政策，AI算力产业链成本与格局重塑(Political Turbulence Distorts Energy Policy, Reshaping Costs and Structure in the AI Computing Industry Chain)", "rating": null, "ticker": null, "analysts": [{"role": 1, "analyst_id": "58020af7-0844-471d-ad19-6b66a73178b6", "sort_order": 1}], "sector_id": null, "coverage_id": null, "region_code": null, "report_type": "macro", "target_price": null, "report_language": "zh", "contact_person_id": null, "investment_thesis": "<p class=\"16\" style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">事件</span></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">在</span>2026<span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">年</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">3</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">月的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">美国</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">参议院辩论中</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">参议院民主党人对共和党的标志性</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">《拯救美国法案》（</span>SAVE America Act<span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">）</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">提出了数百项修正案，其中包括二十多项涉及能源与自然资源问题的提案。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">这些举措是民主党推迟并破坏</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">该</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">争议性</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">选举安全法案</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">努力的一部分。该法案旨在增加非公民在联邦选举中投票的难度，而民主党则认为，这将使数百万美国公民更难行使投票权</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">。目前民主党人提出的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">修正案包括：废除总统唐纳德</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">&middot;</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">特朗普关于能源与气候变化的行政命令；延长某些可再生能源的税收抵免；以及要求数据中心运营商报告其能源与水资源的消耗情况。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">本次民主党在《拯救美国法案》中塞入大量能源相关修正案，本质是一场典型的国会政治博弈，而非真正意义上的能源政策立法。</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"16\" style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">点评</span></span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"16\" style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">能源政策高度政治化，两党共识持续瓦解，长期规划能力被严重削弱。</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">能源议题已深度嵌入美国党派竞争，政策稳定性持续弱化，行业与资本面临的不确定性显著上升。无论是气候目标、电力结构、补贴政策还是监管规则，都越来越成为选举工具，而非基于产业现实与能源安全的理性安排。民主党借能源议题绑定民生情绪、共和党则强调成本与供给稳定，双方在核心方向上难以形成长期一致，导致政策频繁摇摆、预期反复修正。这种环境下，大型能源基建、电网改造、新型电力项目的投资周期被拉长，风险成本抬升，跨周期资本开支意愿明显下降，公用事业与能源产业链整体估值逻辑被迫向</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">&ldquo;短期确定性&rdquo;倾斜。</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"16\" style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">数据中心等高耗能产业的成本规则正在重塑，</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">&ldquo;用者自付&rdquo;将成为长期趋势。</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">伴随</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">AI</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">算力爆发式增长，数据中心用电负荷快速扩张，电网扩容与供电压力持续上升，过去由全民分摊电力基础设施成本的模式难以为继。政策层面正在加速转向</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">&ldquo;谁受益、谁承担&rdquo;的定价机制，数据中心将更多独立承担电网接入、线路扩容、备用容量等相关成本。以</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">100MW</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">数据中心测算：电网接入与扩容成本约</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">亿</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">-1.5</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">亿美元，电价上调</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">15%-20%</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">将带来年电费增加约</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">1000</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">万</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">-1500</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">万美元，全生命周期成本抬升</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">10%-15%</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">。这会直接推高行业整体资本开支与运营成本，倒逼产业向更高能效、绿电配套、储能协同、分布式供能方向升级，低效小型项目逐步出清，行业集中度与技术门槛同步抬升。</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"16\" style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">政策内耗与成本上行，正在缓慢侵蚀美国在全球算力与再工业化竞争中的优势。</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">能源政策不稳定直接拖累电网现代化进度，电力成本刚性上涨又进一步提高制造业与数字产业的运营压力。跨国资本在布局长期算力基地、先进制造产能时，会更加谨慎评估美国市场的政策风险与综合成本。虽然短期仍有产业集群与技术生态支撑，但中长期看，持续的政治博弈与成本抬升，会逐步削弱其整体产业竞争力，也让能源转型与产业升级的节奏慢于潜在最优路径。</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"16\" style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">投资建议</span></span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"15\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">受益北美电网升级与智能调度需求，配网自动化与高压设备订单持续增长的电网智能化与电力设备商如【</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">GE Vernova</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">】、【</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">Eaton</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">】、【</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">Schneider Electric</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">】、【</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">ABB</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">】，数据中心热管理与供电商如【</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">Vertiv</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">】，储能供应商【</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">Tesla</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">】，离网发电制造商如【</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">Bloom Energy</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">】、【潍柴动力】。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"16\" style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">风险</span></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 2.1pt; margin-left: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 13pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #000000; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: #000000; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">能源政策博弈加剧，政策不明确性上升；</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: #000000; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">智能化技术电网应用效果不及预期；</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: #000000; font-size: 16px;\">AI</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: #000000; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">用电需求低于预期。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 5pt 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">In March 2026, Senate Democrats introduced over 20 energy-related amendments to the Republican SAVE America Act (a federal election security bill). These proposals, ranging from rolling back Trump&rsquo;s climate orders to mandating data center energy reporting, aim to delay the bill while highlighting partisan divides over voting rights and energy policy.</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">While unlikely to pass given the GOP majority, these amendments serve two tactical goals: voter alignment, linking voting access to climate/energy costs, and political exposure, forcing Republicans to vote against popular consumer protections.</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">The backdrop is a crisis in energy affordability. With 2025 retail electricity prices jumping 6.7% (far outpacing CPI), the surge in AI data center demand and re-industrialization has made grid-upgrade costs a core 2026 policy issue. While Democrats favor regulation, the GOP&rsquo;s \"Ratepayer Protection Pledge\" forces \"Hyperscalers\" (Amazon, Google, Meta) to fund their own infrastructure. This shifts the U.S. power model from \"socialized costs\" to a \"beneficiary-pays\" system.</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;<span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">We observed </span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">structural certainty in three areas:</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">Grid Modernization</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;Data Center Efficiency/Thermal Management</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">; </span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">Off-grid/Distributed Generation.</span></p>", "certificate_confirmed": true}', 'dff9e78a-d3cb-42f2-ac0c-aaaab2a06fe4/dff9e78a-d3cb-42f2-ac0c-aaaab2a06fe4_002_report_2026-04-02T07-45-29-532Z____________AI_____________AutoRefresh.docx', null, '6de69f70-b17a-48e1-8e49-3efa86b68c40', '2026-04-02 15:45:32.320302+08', '2026-04-02 15:45:32.320302+08', '政治博弈扰动能源政策，AI算力产业链成本与格局重塑_AutoRefresh.docx', null, 'dff9e78a-d3cb-42f2-ac0c-aaaab2a06fe4/dff9e78a-d3cb-42f2-ac0c-aaaab2a06fe4_002_report-pdf_2026-04-02T07-45-31-411Z____________AI_____________AutoRefresh.pdf', '政治博弈扰动能源政策，AI算力产业链成本与格局重塑_AutoRefresh.pdf');
INSERT INTO "public"."report_version" ("id", "report_id", "version_no", "snapshot_json", "word_file_path", "model_file_path", "changed_by", "changed_at", "created_at", "word_file_name", "model_file_name", "pdf_file_path", "pdf_file_name") VALUES 
('a30285d0-cba8-4b8a-8757-a1efedea38bf', '99021d41-55a6-41fb-b4ed-89f704b44fca', '2', '{"title": "2025年年报点评：全年收入强劲增长，飞机交付量走高，均价持续向上(Strong Revenue Growth, Higher Aircraft Deliveries, Rising Average Prices)", "rating": "OUTPERFORM", "ticker": "2507 HK", "analysts": [{"role": 1, "analyst_id": "fb128657-dd0e-4ec1-83c9-9b9f8985c29a", "sort_order": 1}], "sector_id": null, "coverage_id": "6da77705-0093-40c9-b61e-424c3eeb9401", "region_code": null, "report_type": "company", "target_price": "52.45", "report_language": "zh", "contact_person_id": null, "investment_thesis": "<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体; color: #23558c; font-size: 16px;\">西锐飞机是私人航空业的先驱和全球领导者。</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 楷体; font-size: 16px;\">自1984年成立以来，西锐飞机彻底革新了个人航空领域，在全球范围内累计交付了超过10,000架SR2X系列飞机和超过600架Vision Jet。截至2024年底，该公司在私人航空领域占据主导地位，市场份额高达23.2%。在财务表现方面，西锐展现出强劲的营收增长能力，从2020年的5.87亿美元大幅增长至2024年的11.97亿美元；净利润同期从2020年的3600万美元飙升至2024年的1.21亿美元，净利润复合年均增长率（CAGR）高达32.3%。净利率也从2020年的6.2%提高到2024年的10.1%。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体; color: #23558c; font-size: 16px;\">消费者导向场景下私人飞机需求稳健增长。</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 楷体; font-size: 16px;\">通用航空涵盖除军事和定期商业航班之外的所有航空活动，包括私人飞行和专业航空。全球私人飞机市场在交付量和价值方面均实现了稳健增长，平均销售价格也呈现上升趋势。全球私人飞机交付量的持续增长，一方面得益于高净值人群（HNWIs）和飞行学员数量的扩张，另一方面也受到持续基础设施建设的推动。该行业的集中度相当高，西锐尤其在活塞式飞机领域占据领先地位。其两大主要机型系列的市场份额均呈现上升趋势。.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体; color: #23558c; font-size: 16px;\">西锐凭借行业领先的安全性能和全面&ldquo;产品+服务&rdquo;生态系统实现差异化。</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 楷体; font-size: 16px;\"> 西锐的产品线，从SR2X系列到Vision Jet，满足了多样化的市场需求，其中SR系列定位于高端活塞式飞机市场，而Vision Jet则作为涡轮式飞机类别中的高性价比选择。公司的竞争优势源于其开创性的安全功能，包括挽救生命的&ldquo;整机降落伞系统（CAPS）&rdquo;和革命性的&ldquo;安全返航紧急自动着陆系统（Safe Return Emergency Autoland）&rdquo;。关键在于，西锐已超越传统制造业务，发展成为提供全面&ldquo;产品+服务&rdquo;生态系统的企业，涵盖飞行培训、飞机管理和融资等服务。这种高客户留存模式创造了经常性收入并增强了品牌忠诚度，同时带来了高复购率和强大的定价权。 </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体; color: #23558c; font-size: 16px;\">估值与建议</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0cm; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体; font-size: 16px;\">我们预计西锐飞机在2025年至2027年期间的收入将分别达到14.26/16.46/19.28亿美元，净利润分别为1.62/1.99/2.42亿美元。基于贴现现金流（DCF）估值模型，我们首次覆盖并给予&ldquo;优于大市&rdquo;评级，目标价为11.12美元（对应港币86.72元）。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体; color: #23558c; font-size: 16px;\">风险提示</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0cm; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体;\">原材料价格波动；供应链中断；市场竞争加剧；客户需求变化；政策变化.</span></p>", "certificate_confirmed": true}', '99021d41-55a6-41fb-b4ed-89f704b44fca/99021d41-55a6-41fb-b4ed-89f704b44fca_002_report_2026-04-02T07-14-58-722Z_2025__________AutoRefresh.docx', null, '6de69f70-b17a-48e1-8e49-3efa86b68c40', '2026-04-02 15:15:13.28487+08', '2026-04-02 15:15:13.28487+08', '2025年西锐飞机年报点评_AutoRefresh.docx', null, '99021d41-55a6-41fb-b4ed-89f704b44fca/99021d41-55a6-41fb-b4ed-89f704b44fca_002_report-pdf_2026-04-02T07-15-01-133Z___________________AutoRefresh.pdf', '西锐飞机首次覆盖报告（中文）提交版_AutoRefresh.pdf');
