('bb44d1cd-d0a6-4516-9812-65ff1f414a02', 'e1f33554-118d-4893-9fa6-30a1359e53e7', '2', '{"title": "周报(03/23-03/27): 消费板块：港股承压、美股边际修复；互联网板块：政策催化港股分化，美股跌中企稳(Consumption Sector: HK Stocks Under Pressure & US Stocks Show Marginal Recovery; Internet Sector: Policy Catalysts Drive Divergence in HK, US Stocks Exhibit Stabilization Signals Amid Declines)", "rating": null, "ticker": null, "analysts": [{"role": 1, "analyst_id": "58020af7-0844-471d-ad19-6b66a73178b6", "sort_order": 1}], "sector_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000016", "coverage_id": null, "region_code": "HK", "report_type": "sector", "target_price": null, "report_language": "zh", "contact_person_id": null, "investment_thesis": "<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 6pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: #1f497d; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">核心观点</span></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 6pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: #1f497d; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">一、</span></span></strong><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: #1f497d; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: #1f497d; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">海外消费：</span></span></strong><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: #1f497d; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">油价扰动放大波动，港股承压而美股边际修复</span></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 6pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">港股消费：本周板块大幅波动，中证港股通消费主题指数（</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">931454</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">）本周下跌</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">5.10</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">%</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">（截至</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">3/2</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">7</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">），恒生指数本周下跌</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">94</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">%</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">。油价本周剧烈震荡（布伦特冲高至</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">114</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">美元后回落至</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">94</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">美元），地缘不确定性持续压制风险偏好。当前估值进一步回落（</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">931454</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">市盈率</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">P/E2</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">为</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">23.73</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">），安全边际扩大。重点看好高端餐饮、运动服饰及</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">\"</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">以旧换新</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">\"</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">受益股。美股消费：本周小幅反弹，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">XLP</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">上涨</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">0.</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">3</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">%</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">（</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">YTD +</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">4.41</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">%</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">），</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">XLY</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">上涨</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">1.20</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">%</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">（</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">YTD </span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">-8.87</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">%</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">），油价回落预期提振消费板块情绪。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 6pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: #1f497d; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">二、</span></span></strong><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: #1f497d; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: #1f497d; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">海外互联网：</span></span></strong><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: #1f497d; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">港股受政策催化分化演绎，美股科技跌中现企稳信号</span></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 6pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">港股互联网：本周恒生科技指数大幅震荡，累计下跌</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">1.94</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">%</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">，个股分化剧烈。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">月</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">25</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">日国家市场监管总局转发《外卖大战该结束了》，释放外卖行业反</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">\"</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">内卷式竞争</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">\"</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">监管信号，美团当日暴涨</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">13.92%</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">，本周累计上涨</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">8.53</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">%</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">；腾讯（</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">-2.</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">87</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">%</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">）、小米（</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">-</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">0.60</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">%</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">）则随大市回调。南向资金本周大幅波动。美股互联网：地缘谈判反复主导油价及科技股走势，纳斯达克综合指数本周累计下跌</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">1.10%</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">AI</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">产业正从技术研发加速向规模化商业落地演进，长期趋势未变。建议逢低布局兼具云基础设施、数据优势及场景闭环的科技龙头</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 6pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: #1f497d; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">三、</span></span></strong><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: #1f497d; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: #1f497d; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">通用航空：全球交付稳步增长</span></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 6pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">行业复苏：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;2025</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">年全球通用航空器交付量达</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">3,230</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">架（</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">+3.3%</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">），预计</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">2026</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">年将进一步增至</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">3,410</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">架。公务喷气机交付量显著增长（</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">+11.8%</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">），带动交付总价值创历史新高（</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">310</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">亿美元）。竞争格局：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">北美市场主导增长。在活塞及喷气式飞机领域，西锐飞机市场份额持续提升，其中活塞机型市占率达</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">37.2%</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">稳居榜首。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 6pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: #1f497d; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">投资建议：</span></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 6pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">短期市场受地缘博弈及油价剧烈波动影响持续震荡，但中长期逻辑未变。消费板块关注具备品牌护城河与出海能力的龙头，如</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">L'Oreal</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">Ulta Beauty</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">Costco</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">P&amp;G</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">等；互联网科技板块，外卖反内卷监管信号缓解平台补贴压力，叠加</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">AI</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">商业化持续推进，中长期配置价值凸显。坚定看好</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">AI</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">向商业落地转化，我们建议关注美团、阿里巴巴、微软、亚马逊及</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">Alphabet</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">等；通用航空领域，关注市场份额持续扩张的高端制造龙头。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 6pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: #1f497d; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">风险提示：</span></span></strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">地缘政治风险加剧；宏观经济复苏不及预期；</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">AI</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">商业化落地受阻；政策与贸易不确定性。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">Overseas consumption: Oil price volatility amplified market swings, weighing on Hong Kong stocks while U.S. equities saw marginal recovery</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">Hong Kong consumer sector:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;The sector was highly volatile this week. The CSI Hong Kong Stock Connect Consumer Theme Index (931454) fell 5.10% for the week (as of March </span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">27</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">), while the Hang Seng Index declined 1.94%. Oil prices fluctuated sharply during the week, with Brent crude surging to USD 114/bbl before retreating to USD 94/bbl, and ongoing geopolitical uncertainty continued to weigh on risk appetite. Valuations have pulled back further, with the 931454 index now trading at 23.73x P/E2, implying a wider margin of safety. We remain particularly constructive on premium dining, sportswear, and companies benefiting from the consumer trade-in program.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">U.S. consumer sector:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">T</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">he sector posted a modest rebound this week, with XLP up 0.3% (YTD +4.41%) and XLY up 1.20% (YTD -8.87%), as expectations for easing oil prices supported sentiment toward consumer stocks.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 6pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">Overseas internet:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">Hong Kong stocks diverged on policy catalysts, while U.S. tech stocks showed signs of stabilization amid the pullback</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">Hong Kong internet sector: </span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">The Hang Seng Tech Index fluctuated sharply this week, ending down 1.94%, with significant divergence at the stock level. On March 25, China&rsquo;s State Administration for Market Regulation reposted the article &ldquo;The Food Delivery War Should End,&rdquo; sending a regulatory signal against &ldquo;involution-style competition&rdquo; in the food delivery industry. Meituan surged 13.92% on the day and rose 8.53% for the week, while Tencent (-2.87%) and Xiaomi (-0.60%) retreated with the broader market. Southbound capital flows were also highly volatile this week.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">U.S. internet sector:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;Repeated twists in geopolitical negotiations dominated oil prices and tech stock performance. The Nasdaq Composite fell 1.10% for the week, the S&amp;P 500 declined 0.45%, and the Dow Jones rose 0.84%. The AI industry is rapidly evolving from technological development toward large-scale commercialization, and the long-term trend remains intact. We recommend accumulating technology leaders on dips, particularly those with strengths in cloud infrastructure, data advantages, and closed-loop application ecosystems.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 6pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">General aviation:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">Steady global delivery growth</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 6pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">Global general aviation deliveries reached 3,230 units in 2025 (+3.3%) and are expected to rise to 3,410 in 2026. Business jet deliveries grew 11.8%, driving total delivery value to a record USD 31.0 billion. North America remains the key growth driver, while Cirrus continues to gain market share, reaching 37.2% in piston aircraft.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0pt 6pt; text-align: justify; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">Investment recommendations</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 12pt 2.1pt 12pt 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 13pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #000000; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">Markets are likely to remain volatile in the short term amid geopolitical uncertainty and oil price swings, but the medium- to long-term investment thesis remains intact. In consumption, we favor leaders with strong brand moats and global expansion capabilities, such as L&rsquo;Or&eacute;al, Ulta Beauty, Costco, and P&amp;G. In internet and technology, the anti-price-war regulatory signal should help ease subsidy pressure on platforms, while AI commercialization continues to advance. We remain constructive on AI&rsquo;s transition toward large-scale commercialization and recommend focusing on Meituan, Alibaba, Microsoft, Amazon, and Alphabet. In general aviation, we favor high-end manufacturing leaders with expanding market share.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 12pt 2.1pt 12pt 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 13pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #000000; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: #000000; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">Risk Factors:</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 12pt 2.1pt 12pt 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 13pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #000000; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: #000000; font-size: 16px;\">An escalation in geopolitical risks; weaker-than-expected macroeconomic recovery; slower-than-expected AI commercialization; and policy and trade uncertainty.</span></p>", "certificate_confirmed": true}', 'e1f33554-118d-4893-9fa6-30a1359e53e7/e1f33554-118d-4893-9fa6-30a1359e53e7_002_report_2026-04-02T08-18-25-935Z____________3_23-3_27_AutoRefresh.docx', null, '6de69f70-b17a-48e1-8e49-3efa86b68c40', '2026-04-02 16:18:34.708107+08', '2026-04-02 16:18:34.708107+08', '全球消费及互联网周报_3_23-3_27_AutoRefresh.docx', null, 'e1f33554-118d-4893-9fa6-30a1359e53e7/e1f33554-118d-4893-9fa6-30a1359e53e7_002_report-pdf_2026-04-02T08-18-33-002Z____________3_23-3_27_AutoRefresh.pdf', '全球消费及互联网周报_3_23-3_27_AutoRefresh.pdf');
