('dc1d3cfe-07df-4a8c-9c13-9e3defb8a745', 'f9716855-5886-4df2-b68f-5eb7d1c54fd6', '2', '{"title": "全球国防与航空航天周报(03/15-03/21):航空发动机价格延续涨势，美国\"金穹\"反导提速，全球防务采购聚焦一体化防空与智能无人平台(Aircraft engine prices up, \"Golden Dome\" accelerated, global defense focuses on integrated air defense & unmanned platforms)", "rating": null, "ticker": null, "analysts": [{"role": 1, "analyst_id": "58020af7-0844-471d-ad19-6b66a73178b6", "sort_order": 1}], "sector_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000087", "coverage_id": null, "region_code": "HK", "report_type": "sector", "target_price": null, "report_language": "zh", "contact_person_id": null, "investment_thesis": "<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: #1f497d; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">核心观点：</span></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: #1f497d; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">全球国防与航空航天：</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">美国：飞机发动机和发动机部件制造价格指数</span>2026<span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">年</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">2</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">月为</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">277.110</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">，环比</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">+0.03%</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">，同比增长</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">1.07%</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">。飞机发动机和发动机零部件制造：飞机发动机零部件价格指数</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">2026</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">年</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">2</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">月为</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">293.396</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">，环比</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">+0.05%</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">，同比增长</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">1.41%</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">。美国政府支出国防价格指数</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">2025</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">年</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">Q4</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">为</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">120.187</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">，环比</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">+0.9%</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">，同比增长</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">2.95%</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">本周航空航天领域在民航供应链优化、航空安全监管升级、商用飞机交付安排、旋翼机市场回暖以及深空探测科研五大方向同步取得重要进展。波音要求供应商评估中东局势对生产链可能造成的扰动，英国航空延长中东航线调整，多家欧洲与非洲航空公司面临燃油价格和供应压力；</span>FAA <span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">收紧主要机场周边直升机运行规定，进一步强化航空安全管理标准。</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">Ryanair </span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">对 </span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">737 MAX 10 </span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">的认证与交付前景保持乐观，</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">Airbus </span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">警示欧洲关键技术投入不足，显示商用航空竞争正加速向产能扩张、技术革新和运营效率提升纵深推进；</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">NASA Perseverance </span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">在火星发现古老流水迹象，拓宽了深空探测的科学视野。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">本周全球国防领域在北美、欧洲和中东三大战略方向同步推进关键防务举措。美国加大</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">&ldquo;Golden Dome&rdquo;</span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">天基反导系统建设与承包商协调力度，强化战略威慑能力；欧洲围绕 </span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri;\">FCAS </span><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">战斗机项目及联合军购机制推进技术整合与采购效率优化，强化跨国协同；西班牙与乌克兰在无人机、雷达、防空及导弹系统领域签署多项合作协议，加快实战化能力建设；中东和瑞士则加速部署防空、反无人机及网络防御体系，提升区域威慑与信息化作战能力。整体来看，全球防务采购正向一体化防空网络、智能无人作战平台、先进空战系统及综合指挥控制能力集中，行业呈现短期订单释放与长期结构优化并行的发展态势。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: #1f497d; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">投资建议：</span></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: #1f497d; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">随着航空航天业的稳健复苏、国防支出增加及军事现代化需求，我们建议关注高性能结构部件制造商</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">Howmet Aerospace</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">、航空航天零部件专业制造商</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">Loar Holdings</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">、法国航空发动机巨头赛峰</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">(SAFRY)</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">、领先国防承包商雷神技术</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">(RTX)</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">及以色列国防电子龙头</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">Elbit Systems</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">。随着民用航空器维护需求增加，我们建议关注</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">VSE</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">技术服务公司</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: #1f497d; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">风险提示：</span></span></strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">地缘政治冲突升级导致防务采购优先级突变；国防预算审议进程存在不确定性，项目拨款到位时间或有所滞后</span>;</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">卫星星座组网进度受发射排期及在轨测试影响，商业运营时点或晚于预期</span>; <span style=\";font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">商业航天运力供给增加，发射服务价格面临一定下行压力。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">Global Defense &amp; Aerospace</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">Price Indices: </span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">The U.S. aircraft engine and engine parts manufacturing price index was 277.110 in February 2026, up 0.03% MoM and 1.07% YoY; aircraft engine components price index stood at 293.396, up 0.05% MoM and 1.41% YoY. The U.S. government defense spending price index was 120.187 in Q4 2025, up 0.9% QoQ and 2.95% YoY.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">Aerospace</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">Commercial Space: </span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">Boeing asked suppliers to assess Middle East supply risks; British Airways adjusted routes, and European/African airlines faced fuel pressures. FAA tightened helicopter rules near major airports. Ryanair stayed optimistic on 737 MAX 10 delivery; Airbus warned of underinvestment in key European technologies. NASA&rsquo;s Perseverance found ancient water flows on Mars.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">Defense</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\" align=\"justify\"><strong style=\";font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">Defense Budget: </span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 16px;\">U.S. advanced the \"Golden Dome\" missile defense and contractor coordination; Europe streamlined FCAS integration and joint procurement; Spain and Ukraine expanded cooperation on drones, radar, air defense, and missiles; the Middle East and Switzerland accelerated air, counter-UAV, and cyber defense deployments. Global defense procurement is focusing on integrated air defense, intelligent unmanned platforms, advanced air combat systems, and command and control, with short-term orders and long-term structural upgrades progressing in parallel.</span></p>", "certificate_confirmed": true}', 'f9716855-5886-4df2-b68f-5eb7d1c54fd6/f9716855-5886-4df2-b68f-5eb7d1c54fd6_002_report_2026-04-02T10-15-24-540Z_______________0315-0321____________________________________________AutoRefresh.docx', null, '6de69f70-b17a-48e1-8e49-3efa86b68c40', '2026-04-02 18:15:26.61412+08', '2026-04-02 18:15:26.61412+08', '华福国际全球国防和航空航天（0315-0321)：航空发动机价格延续涨势，美国金穹反导提速，全球防务采购聚焦一体化防空与智能无人平台_AutoRefresh.docx', null, 'f9716855-5886-4df2-b68f-5eb7d1c54fd6/f9716855-5886-4df2-b68f-5eb7d1c54fd6_002_report-pdf_2026-04-02T10-15-26-209Z_______________0315-0321____________________________________________AutoRefresh.pdf', '华福国际全球国防和航空航天（0315-0321)：航空发动机价格延续涨势，美国金穹反导提速，全球防务采购聚焦一体化防空与智能无人平台_AutoRefresh.pdf');
